\ip Judaba, kantri Babilon…®n kalabus ategha ua Jerusalem…®n izez…®, Hagai Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a gan…®ngizir akar kam…®n gun me m…®gei. Me azenir mabar Jerusalem…®n ikia, zuam…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n ingarizir puvat…®. Ez…® Hagai ko, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Sekaraia, aning Serubabel, ko Josuan, n…®ghn…®ziba fasa akabar aning…®n m…®gei. Aning Judabar gumazir dapanimning. Eght…® aning God…®n D…®penim uam an ingars…® Judabar gumazamizibav kemegh, uaghan God…®n ziam fer arazim…®n arazir kuraba ak…®ram. 
\ip Hagai kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, Judaba ingangarir kam damuam, a men akuraght…®, me uari ko ingarir arazir kam bar deragham. Eght…® God…®n akar d…®k…®r…®ziba, an akam inigha izezir gumaziba m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, da guizbang…®rama otivam. Eght…® God bar deragh uan gumazamizibar amut…®, me dughiar bar aghuarimra ikiam. 
\c 1  
\ms1 God uan D…®penim…®n ingarasa gumazamizibav gei 
\mr (Sapta 1:1--2:9) 
\s1 God ua uan D…®penim…®n ingarasa gumazamizibar av…®si 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Esra 4:24--5:2; Esra 6:14\x*Dughiar kam…®n Darius, Persian kantrin atrivir ekiam…®n itima, an namba 2…®n azenim. Ez…® an iak…®nir namba 6…®n, an aruer faragha zuim…®n aven, Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®g…®r…®g…®am isa, uan akam inigha izir gumazim Hagai gan…®ngi. Eght…® an akar kam is…® Judabar gumazir dapanim Serubabel dan…®ngam, a Sealtiel…®n otarim. Egh uaghan akar kam is…® Jehosadak…®n otarim Josua, a Judabar ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim dan…®ngam.\f + \fr 1:1 \ft Azenir kam 520, an azenir fom…®ra Krais…®n dughiam…®n ikezim, an dughiam Ogas 29.\f* 
\v 2 Egha Hagai kamagh…®n aning m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòGumazamizir kaba ghaze, ‚ÄúGod…®n D…®penim…®n ingaramim dughiam t…®ghar magh…®n otivam.‚Äù ‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\p  
\v 3 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, gumazamizibav k…®masa m…®g…®r…®g…®aba isa ua Hagai gan…®ngi.  
\v 4 A ghaze, ‚ÄúNan gumazamiziba, ia manmaghsua uari bagha d…®penir bar aghuibar ingara dar itima, nan d…®penim ikuvigha iti?  
\v 5 Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, dat…®r…®gh…®n ghaze, Ia bizir kurar ia bativir kabar gara n…®ghn…®si o puvat…®?  
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt God…®n Araziba 28:38-40; Hosea 8:7; Hagai 2:16\x*Ia dagher av…®riba oparigha, dar dagher av…®riba isir puvat…®. Ia apava izevir puvat…®. Ia d…®paba apava, kuariba ian p…®rav…®ra iti. Ia korotiaba ikia da aghuava, arugharughv…®ra ikiam. Gumazir dag…®aba bagha ingara da isiba, da zuam…®ra gefi, mati ia da isa dag…®avtarir toriba itibagh azui.  
\v 7 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®gei, ia bizir kurar ia bativir kabar gara n…®ghn…®si, o puvat…®?  
\v 8 Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim ghaze, Ia m…®ghs…®abar mavanang temeba okegh izighir…® nan D…®penim uam an ingarigh. Eght…® nan navir averiam deragh bar akongegham. Egh ia an aven nan ziam f…®t…®, k…® uan angazangarim ko, gavgavim saram otogh, ziar bar ekiam iniam. 
\p  
\v 9 ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim ghaze, Ia nan D…®penim ataghiz…® a ikuvigha itima, ia uari uan d…®penibar ingarigha arui. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia uan azenibar dagher ekiataba inis…® damuva avegham. Ia dagher muziarir kaba inigh agheght…®, k…® dagh iveraght…® da zuam…®ra gevegham.  
\v 10 Ian arazir kaba bang…®n, ghuariaba irir puvat…®z…®ma dagheba ian azenibar otivir puvat…®.  
\v 11 K…® uab…® amozim…®n anogoroke. Egha k…® aruer ekiam gamiz…®, a nguazim koma, m…®ghs…®aba ko, ian wit…®n azeniba, ian wain…®n azeniba, ian oliv…®n temeba, nguazim…®n otivava aghuir zuravariba, ian as…®ziba, gumazamiziba ko, me oparir dagher guar av…®riba, a bar dagh apongez…® da m…®s…®ngi.‚Äù 
\s1 Gumazamiziba God…®n akam baregha an g…®n zui 
\p  
\v 12 Dughiar kam…®n, Judabar gumazir dapanim Serubabel, a Sealtiel…®n otarim ko, Josua Jehosadak…®n otarim, a ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim ko, Judan gumazamizir ua izegha aning ko itir vabara, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God, men God, an m…®g…®r…®g…®aba baraki. Egha me an akam inigha izir gumazim Hagain m…®g…®r…®g…®aba baregha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n atiatingi. Me fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, anemadaz…®ma a izi.  
\v 13 Ez…® Hagai, an akam inigha izir gumazim, a kamagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam…®n gun gumazamizibav gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God ghaze, ‚ÄòK…® ia koma akam ak…®ra ghaze, k…® zurara ia ko ikiam.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Judabar gumazir dapanim Serubabel, a Sealtiel…®n otarim ko, Josua a Jehosadak…®n otarim, a ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim ko, Judan gumazamizir aning ko itir vabara, men n…®ghn…®ziba ua da fema, me iza ua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, a men God, me an D…®penim ingari.  
\v 15 Darius atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, an azenir pumuning…®n namba 6 iak…®nim…®n dughiar namba 24…®n, me ingangarir kam foregha a gami.\f + \fr 1:15 \ft Azenir kam 520, an azenir fom…®ra Krais…®n dughiam…®n ikezim, an dughiam Septemba 21.\f* 
\c 2  
\s1 God…®n D…®penir igiam bar deragham 
\p  
\v 1 Darius atrivim…®n itir azenir namba 2…®n, an iak…®nir namba 7…®n, dughiar namba 21…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God uam akam isa, akam inigha izir gumazim Hagai gan…®ngi.\f + \fr 2:1 \ft Dughiar kam, a Oktoba 17.\f* 
\v 2 God Hagai m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® mang…® Judabar gumazir dapanim Serubabel Sealtiel…®n otarim ko, Josua Jehosadak…®n otarim, a ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim ko, Judan ikiav…®ra itir varazira, kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m suam,  
\v 3 \x - \xo 2:3 \xt Esra 3:12; Sekaraia 4:10\x*‚ÄòFom…®ra nan D…®penim…®n ganganim bar dera, ez…® ian tarazi ti an ganigha a g…®n…®ghn…®ghav…®ra ikiama? Dat…®r…®gh…®n ia an gari, a kamagh…®ra garav…®ra iti o, a pura bizir k…®nim…®n m…®n iti?  
\v 4 Ikiav…®ra Itir God ghaze, O Serubabel, n…® tugh gavgafigh. O Josua, Jehosadak…®n otarim, n…® ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim, n…® tugh gavgafigh. Ia nguazir kam…®n itir gumazamiziba, ia tuivigh gavgafigh. Guizbang…®ra, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim ghaze, k…® ia ko iti, kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia d…®kavigh ua ingangarim damu.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt Ua Me Ini 29:45-46\x*Ia fom…®ra Isip ategha azenan izasava amima, k…® ia ko Akar Gavgavim ak…®ra ghaze, k…® ia ko zurara ikiam. Guizbang…®ra nan Duam ian tong…®n ikiav…®ra iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia atiatingan mark…®. 
\p  
\v 6 \x - \xo 2:6 \xt Joel 3:16; Hagai 2:21; Hibru 12:26\x*‚Äú‚Äâ‚ÄòKar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim kamagh…®n m…®gei. Dughiar otevim…®n, k…® ua overiam ko, nguazim ko, ongarim ko, nguazir m…®diarim…®n itir bizibagh nobaghnobagham.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt Aisaia 60:4-9; Daniel 2:44\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim ghaze, K…® kantrin igharazibagh nuabaght…® me akong, uan bizir aghuir ivezir bar p…®n koziba inigh kagh iz…®t…®, nan D…®penim ganganir aghuim damuam.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 2:8 \xt 1 Eghaghaniba 29:14-16\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim ghaze, Kantriba bar dar itir silvaba ko golba, da bar nan biziba.  
\v 9 Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim ghaze, Nan D…®penir igiar kam an ganganim ko, ziar ekiam bar deragh, nan D…®penir ghurim gafiragham. Eght…® k…® bizir av…®riba gumazamizibar an…®ngt…®, me navir am…®rizim ko, dabirabir aghuim ikiam. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n gavgaviba Bar Itim, k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\ms1 God deragh gumazamiziba ko, gumazir dapanim Serubabel, damuam 
\mr (Sapta 2:10-23) 
\s1 Arazir m…®z…®r…®ziba gumazamizibar ofabagh as…®ghas…®si 
\p  
\v 10 Darius atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, an azenir namba 2…®n, iak…®nir namba 9…®n, an dughiar 24…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, m…®g…®r…®g…®ar mam ua Hagai gan…®ngi.\f + \fr 2:10 \ft Azenir kam 520, an azenir fom…®ra Krais…®n dughiam…®n otozir dughiam, an dughiam Disemba 18.\f* 
\v 11 Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® nan azangs…®zir kam…®n m…®ngarim g…®foghfoghs…®, ofa bagh amir gumazibar azaragh, Moses Osirizir Araziba manmagh…®n m…®gei.  
\v 12 Gumazitam, God gan…®ngizir ofa gamir as…®zir tuzitam inigh, uan korotiam…®n aven anerugh mang…®t…®, an korotiar otevitam bret…®n tam o, dagher isamiziba o, wain o, oliv…®n borem o, dagher guar igharagha garitam uaghan a seregh mang…®t…®, dagher kam God baghv…®ra ik…® bar anogoregham o puvat…®gham?‚Äù Ez…® Hagai ghua ofa gamir gumazibar azaraz…® me kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúMamagh…®n puvat…®gham.‚Äù\f + \fr 2:12 \ft N…® Ofa Gami 6:25-27…®n ganigh.\f* 
\p  
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt D…®boboniba 19:11-22\x*Ez…® Hagai ua men azara, ‚ÄúGumazitam uan dafarim is…® gumazir kuatam gis…®n dat…®gh, g…®n daghebar suiraght…®, dagher kaba God…®n damazim…®n m…®zegham, o puvat…®gham?‚Äù Ez…® ofa gamir gumaziba ghaze, ‚ÄúAre, da m…®zegham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…® Hagai kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God ghaze, ‚ÄòGumazamizir kaba ko, men kantrin me amir biziba nan damazim…®n kamagh…®ra ghue. Men n…®ghn…®ziba ko, me amir araziba m…®ze. Kamagh…®ra ofan me ofa gamir dakozim…®n amiba, da bar mogh…®ra nan damazim…®n m…®ze.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\s1 God uan gumazamiziba deragh me damuasa akam ak…®ri 
\p  
\v 15 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ghaze, ‚ÄúIa t…®ghar nan d…®penim…®n ingaramin dughiam, faragha ia bativizir biziba ia dagh n…®ghn…®gh.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 2:16 \xt Hagai 1:6; 1:10-11; Sekaraia 8:10-12\x*Dughiar kam…®n bizir maba ia batifi. Ia dagher pozir mam aghuasa ghua ghaze, ia 4plan daghevtaribar aghuigham. Ez…® puvat…®, ia daghevtarir pumuningrama aghui. Ia ghaze, ia ti wain…®n teng…®n ekiam…®n mang…®gh, 10plan m…®neba tuigham. Ez…® puvat…®, ia m…®ner 4plara tui.  
\v 17 Ikiav…®ra Itir God ghaze, K…® am…®nir gavgavir fefeim itim ko, ar…®mariar kurar mam ko, ais…®n amozir kuram amadaz…®, da izaghirava ian dagher ia oparizibagh as…®ghas…®ki. Ia bizir kabar gara navibagh ighasa n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®.  
\v 18 Dat…®r…®gh…®n namba 9…®n iak…®nim…®n, an 24…®n dughiam ia nan D…®penim…®n ingarasa, dag…®ar ekiaba isa D…®penim…®n apengan ik…®, gavgavim a dan…®ngasa da ar…®ki. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, dat…®r…®gh…®n ia bizir aghuir k…® damuamibar ganam.  
\v 19 Guizbang…®ra, ian dagher d…®penir ekiar dagheba ar…®ziba, dat…®r…®gh…®n witba dar puvat…®. Eght…® ian wain…®n ikar…®ziba ko, figh…®n temeba ko, pomigranet…®n temeba ko, oliv…®n temeba, da t…®ghar bam. Dat…®r…®gh…®n ikegh mang…®, k…® bar deraghv…®ra ia damuam.‚Äù 
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ziar ekiam is…® Serubabel dan…®ngam 
\p  
\v 20 Dughiar kamra, iak…®nir kamran an dughiar 24…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a uam Hagai m…®gei,  
\v 21 ‚ÄúN…® Judabar gumazir dapanim Serubabel, kamagh…®n a m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòK…® overiam ko, nguazim…®n itir biziba ua dagh inobagh inobaghasava ami.  
\v 22 K…® kantrin igharaziba ko, atrivibar gavgaviba ag…®vagham, egh karisba igh…®raright…®, dar karisbar suizir gumaziba da sara daighiregham. Eght…® hoziaba ar…®m…®ghireght…®, men m…®dorozir gumaziba d…®kavigh kagh…®ra uan roroabav sogh bar me agevegham.  
\v 23 Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim ghaze, O Serubabel, nan ingangarir gumazim, Sealtiel…®n otarim, dughiar kam otoght…®, k…® n…® inight…® n…® guizbang…®ra nan ziam…®n gumazamizibagh ativagh men ganam. K…® n…®rara am…®sefe, ez…® n…® mati nan atrivim…®n ziar ekiam ko, gavgaviba akaghamin ring…®n nan dafarim…®n itim…®n m…®n ikia, gumazamiziba geghuvamin gavgavim iti. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim nan m…®g…®r…®g…®aba kamagh…®ra tu.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù